title: Unboxing The World's Smallest Phone
description:
The Most RIDICULOUS MacBook Pro
https://youtu.be/46qTg3swoEo?list=PL7u4lWXQ3wfI_7PgX0C-VTiwLeu0S4v34

The Tiny T1 is the World's smallest phone. This thing is shockingly small, unbelievably small. It's just slightly taller than an SD card and when compared to a full size smartphone it's dwarfed. The Tiny T1 features 3 days of standby time or 3 hours of talk time. It's obviously a novelty device but nonetheless impressive... Even to the person that has everything.
